# Concrete tools live here: domain/tools/<Name>Tool.luau
#
# Each returns a value satisfying domain/tool/Tool.luau's `Tool` type and is
# registered in domain/tool/ToolRegistry.luau. See ARCHITECTURE.md §6.4 for
# the canonical "add a tool" recipe. No tool is scaffolded yet (this delivery
# is doc + skeleton, not a sample tool).
